results into the permanent possibility of ...d5-d4, only Black can be better.})
(10. cxd5 Nxd5 {This is an operation we have come accross many times.} 11. Bg3
(11. Bxe7 Qxe7 12. Rc1 c5 $11) 11... c5 12. Nxd5 exd5 $5 13. b3 (13. Ne5 Nxe5
14. Bxe5 c4 15. Bc2 f6 16. Bf4 f5 17. Be5 b5 18. f4 Bc8 19. Rf3 Bf6 20. Rg3 Qe8
