but fortunately there were no consequences for the final result.} (38... fxe6
39. Rxe6 Rxa5 40. Rxh6 Rb5 $11) 39. Rf2 {Oops!} Rxa5 40. Rxf7+ Ke8 41. Kf4 Rb5
{½-½ Neverov,V (2485)-Marin,M (2603) Jerusalem 2015} *

