got into trouble, Grunberg, S (2385)-Beliavsky, A (2590) Bucharest 1980 (0-1, 60)
}) 30. Rxc8 Rxc8 31. Rxd3 Bxb4 $1 {The point. Black simply wins a pawn.} 32.
Qxb4 $2 {The thematical but losing continuation.} Rc1+ 33. Kh2 Nxf2 34. Ra3
Rh1+ 35. Kg3 Ne4+ 36. Kg4 h5# *

